{"tid":1162246,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"直升機嘉道理農場後山墜毀　男機師死亡","createTime":"2019-05-19T17:58:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T18:32:13.000Z","uid":7828,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5f7395451a203f099a59e6dfb6ff218021dc4721","tid":1162246,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:58:47.000Z","msg":"一架直升機在八鄉嘉道理農場附近山坡墜毀，一名男機師死亡，消防初步相信是機頭起火，但成因仍有待調查。<br />\n<br />\n現場是嘉道理農場辦公室後方的山坡，直升機墜毀後有市民拍攝到大量濃煙升上半空，並傳出多下爆炸聲。墜毀的直升機完全燒焦，剩下一堆殘骸，消防射水降溫，部分懷疑是直升機的零件更飛到農場外面馬路，飛行服務隊直升機在上空盤旋。<br />\n<br />\n直升機約四點九在石崗機場起飛，消防約四十五分鐘後接報墜毀，到場發現一名男機師死亡，意外原因有待調查，死者家屬到場與香港飛行總會主席到場了解情況。<br />\n<br />\n涉事的是Robinson R44型號的四座輕型直升機，民航處表示直升機機齡、機師當時的飛行目的仍然有待調查。<br />\n<br />\n雖然已經入夜，但調查工作仍在進行，暫時未知道在何時完結，嘉道理農場宣布星期一將會暫停開放。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=348579\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D348579&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ1xUxn6Ez5IAhGrAWUjzTwv4%3D&h=3e7ad02c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D348579&h=b486455e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=348579</a>"},{"pid":"2c93da777ea18b52de06ee0adead148a53f222e1","tid":1162246,"uid":7516,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T18:00:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2616553212bdd2eb95f45305d3f88c69385f06a0","tid":1162246,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T18:25:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港第一次"},{"pid":"6ba581bfff18058bc4b4a1be79fe84cdca0eaa71","tid":1162246,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T18:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abb1276002e5d3e1d4951c82e16df731f8865123","tid":1162246,"uid":127947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T18:32:13.000Z","msg":"點解地點唔係禮賓府....."}]}